{"tid":1458932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要攞返主動權同話語權","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:23:04.000Z","uid":42870,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ebfed879733dc3283e26871501ac473680781c","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"基於好多淺藍同中立撚而家仲係覺得我地成日突然出黎攪事，覺得政府想對話但係我地又唔肯。<br />\n建議每次有大型行動前都要set deadline 要政府答應5大訴求。例如聽日2點前唔答應5大訴求，3點就癱瘓xx。<br />\n雖然明知佢唔會應承，但係咁樣會形做出係政府唔回應先導致升級，將個波交返比佢。不停重覆久而久之就可以將政府係沖擊事件上面既責任加大。<br />\n而set deadline 我建議用啲公開啲既形式通知政府，例如發公開信，要等全世界人都知係政府唔理。"},{"pid":"aaf40131f907852f291d0e4fbba64d8a2192a145","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bb1e7e6b947ba901659080e6c9f0ad61c0cc7ffe","tid":1458932,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"我反而希望admin留意返近期新用戶加入既數量。同動作。呢度好小會busy。大家明"},{"pid":"cff186651d73db9f51fd03636a0ddad16f629b03","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"17d5418ceb82a4593369a3af4fb73f7c3d71e3b7","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"129bc6c95edc6c59d9859a45017adf7be1403e5c","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6a0f1994369fea26cf5132712e4aeb2ba4ac17e3","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7e95f485c62f2e16efee6d49c95ee7202cfc8f9d","tid":1458932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fbd09ed306786b5275feb9c8bd14f48ff747cf1a","tid":1458932,"uid":160180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:43:32.00